      "name": "Merge Sort",
      "formula": "T(n) = 2T(n/2) + O(n) → O(n log n)",
      "example": "Always n log n, uses O(n) space"
    },
    {
      "id": "f2",
      "name": "Quick Sort Average",
      "formula": "T(n) = 2T(n/2) + O(n) → O(n log n)",
      "example": "Worst: T(n) = T(n-1) + O(n) → O(n²)"
    }
  ]
